    @Service
 @Properties(value=@Property(name="process.label",value="XMP Writeback"))
public class XMPWritebackProcess
extends AbstractAssetWorkflowProcess
    XMPWritebackProcess writes back meta data to the original binary

    This process is executed on any changes made under the metadata node {/content/dam(...)/metadata}.
